hopobject.body: I'll text you later vps.net The entire England squad has been snubbed, by the Dalai Lama no less. Seriously, though, today we took advantage of a day off to soak up the spirituality of Dharamsala. After our trip up to McLeod Ganj, I've realised that there is only one person more famous around here than the Dalai Lama â and that's Kevin Pietersen. We were mobbed so much that in the end we had to beat a retreat back to the team hotel.
